            <h1 id="parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-for-family-support-housing-and-child-maintenance">Parliamentary Under Secretary of State for Family Support, Housing and Child Maintenance</h1>
            <div class="govspeak">
<p>The ministerâ€™s responsibilities include:</p>

<ul>
  <li>cross-<abbr title="Department for Work and Pensions">DWP</abbr> Commons spokesperson</li>
  <li>workless families, relationship support and support for disadvantaged groups</li>
